{
  "schemaVersion": "1.0",
  "ueVersion": "5.7",
  "type": "Material",
  "name": "stress_all_nodes",
  "description": "Multi-dimensional EXPORT stress test of the final UE T3D output. Covers every currently-exportable node type PLUS known export-gap nodes: Named Reroute (Declaration/Usage, heavy use), and the dynamic-pin nodes SetMaterialAttributes / GetMaterialAttributes / LandscapeLayerBlend. Also stresses emitter edge cases: long linear chains, high fan-out, duplicate-into-one-OUT-pin (dup-drop warning), float extremes (1e-7 / 1e21), special characters in Custom.Code/Description and comment text, ComponentMask/AppendVector channel masks, and every MaterialOutput attribute pin wired. NOTE: this material intentionally surfaces export warnings (it is no longer \"zero warnings\").",
